### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/healthz

### Create Driver
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Akmal Karimov",
  "phone": "+998901234567",
  "license_number": "AB1234567",
  "car_model": "Chevrolet Nexia",
  "car_plate": "01A123BC",
  "status": "active"
}

### Get Driver by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}

### List All Drivers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers?page=1&limit=20

### List Active Drivers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers?status=active&page=1&limit=20

### Search Drivers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers?search=Akmal&page=1&limit=20

### Update Driver
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "car_model": "Chevrolet Gentra",
  "phone": "+998991234567"
}

### Update Driver Status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "inactive"
}

### Delete Driver (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}

### Log Driver Activity - Go Online
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}/activity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "went_online",
  "notes": "Started shift at downtown station"
}

### Log Driver Activity - Go Offline
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}/activity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "went_offline",
  "notes": "End of shift"
}

### Get Driver Activity Log
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}/activity?page=1&limit=20

### Get Driver Working Hours
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/{{driver_id}}/working-hours?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-31

### Get Active Drivers Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/stats/active

### Error Cases

### Create Driver - Invalid Phone
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test Driver",
  "phone": "123456",
  "license_number": "TEST123",
  "car_model": "Test Car",
  "car_plate": "TEST123"
}

### Create Driver - Missing Fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test Driver"
}

### Create Driver - Duplicate Phone
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Another Driver",
  "phone": "+998901234567",
  "license_number": "XY9876543",
  "car_model": "Cobalt",
  "car_plate": "02B456CD"
}

### Get Non-existent Driver
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Update with Invalid ID
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/invalid-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "car_model": "New Model"
}
